@NODE "Intro"

Introducing VirtualLink
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  VirtualLink was written primarily to establish a virtual ethernet link
  between MacTCP and Miami Deluxe when running a Macintosh emulator. This
  allows you to use Macintosh internet applications without stealing the
  modem away from Amiga internet applications. It might have other uses as
  well.
@ENDNODE

